{"id":394,"slug":"something-sometime-someone","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/events/something-sometime-someone/","title":"Something Sometime Someone","company":"Rushali","genre":"Comedy","description":"How baffling that people hear Charlie as she enunciates her name Rushali (ROO-SHA-LEE) - In this debut comedy hour a cacophony unveils as you uncover that yes it is rude to call an Indian Aunty - “a peanut eating pachyderm”. Just like New York City’s sewer covers, Rushali was made in India - right in the heart of Bollywood - Mumbai. She smuggled herself(legally) into the USA in her twenties only to find herself in Amsterdam’s comedy scene (no, not the red light district.. cmon.. what a cliche!) attempting to make the Dutch laugh - a feat not for the faint hearted. As she navigates this world wondering if her dead grandmother is controlling it - she pays homage to Bollywood as one rightfully must when they are born dancing to it's tunes.","duration_minutes":60,"age_suitability":"18+","image_url":"https://content.brightonfringe.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/02-26-2026-112433-3419.jpg","website":"","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/brightonfringe/","twitter":"https://twitter.com/brightonfringe","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/brightonfringefestival","accessibility_features":["Assistance Dog"],"content_warnings":["Immigration","Loud"],"cast":[],"scraped_at":"2026-05-19T09:31:56.536460","venue":{"id":3,"slug":"grania-dean-studio-lantern-theatre-act","name":"Grania Dean Studio (Lantern Theatre @ ACT)","address":"77 St James Street, East Susssex","url":"https://www.brightonfringe.org/venues/grania-dean-studio-lantern-theatre-act","lat":50.82022702785896,"lng":-0.13063054104227145},"performances":[{"id":25336,"date":"2026-05-31","time":"","standard_price":null,"concession_price":null,"is_sold_out":false,"booking_url":""},{"id":25337,"date":"2026-05-22","time":"23:00","standard_price":15.0,"concession_price":null,"is_sold_out":false,"booking_url":""},{"id":25